    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project with this budget-friendly find! While it definitely shows its age and will need some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back to its best, it's a fantastic opportunity for a fixer-upper or a handy driver looking for a bargain. This car is sold as-is and is waiting for someone with the right touch to give it a second life!",
      "price": 7500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
